item.title: CVE-2023-4284|2024-08-02T07:24:04.598Z -- unknown -- post%20timeline
item.description: The Post Timeline WordPress plugin before 2.2.6 does not sanitise and escape an invalid nonce before outputting it back in an AJAX response, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against high privilege users such as admin
